parameters              NONE
rattle                  WATER

vdwtype                 LENNARD-JONES
radiusrule              ARITHMETIC
radiustype              R-MIN
radiussize              RADIUS
epsilonrule             GEOMETRIC
electric                332.0522173
dielectric              1.0000

## OPC Parameters (J Phys Chem Lett, 5, 3863-3871, 2014)

