atom             3    M     "OPC Water M"     0       0.000     1

bond             1    2                  1000.0      0.8724
bond             1    3                  1000.0      0.1594
bond             2    2                  1000.0      1.3712
angle            2    1    2              100.0      103.60
angle            2    1    3              100.0       51.80
angle            1    2    2              100.0       38.20
torsion          0    1    2    0

vdw              1                      1.77717      0.2128
vdw              2                        0.000      0.0000
vdw              3                        1.000      0.0000

charge           1                        0.000
charge           2                       0.6791
charge           3                      -1.3582
